## ðŸ”— Dependencies

Core dependencies:

- `pymilvus>=2.5.4` - Vector database integration
- `fabricatio-core` - Core interfaces and utilities

Rust extensions:

- TEI client bindings
- Protobuf definitions for gRPC communication

